title: Trickbag - Tailor Made 2006
description:
For over 16 years now Trickbag has amazed audiences all over Scandinavia, Europe & the US with their energetic live-shows and CDs all containing original songs. Nowadays Trickbag is regarded a top act on the Swedish Blues scene and is well known for being one of the best back-up bands in the business. The band has become the number 1 choice for numerous Blues artists when touring in Europe, such as: Kid Ramos, John Nemeth, Barrelhouse Chuck, Gene Taylor, 'Little George' Sueref, etc. Trickbag has also shared stages with stars like: Kim Wilson, Jackie Payne, Kirk Fletcher, Earl Thomas, Sven Zetterberg etc etc. Their latest record 'Tailor-Made' was voted 'Swedens Best Blues Album' featuring Gene Taylor on Piano & Organ. (bluebeatmusic.com)
